  "description": "feliX performing a solo. Soprano formant with strong effort pushes into operatic belt territory — but the drama stays moderate so partials retain their individual character. Fast vibrato and bright tilt give the classic neon-tetra sparkle. Filter envelope responds to velocity for expressive phrasing. A colorful, confident lead voice with personality.",
